      "text": "## Ollama phi4:14b\n192.168.1.56:11434\nScanner estimates ($0)"
    },
    {
      "id": "claude-api",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -600,
      "y": -60,
      "width": 220,
      "height": 80,
      "color": "5",
      "text": "## Claude Sonnet 4\nAnthropic API\nBrain only (~$0.02/eval)"
    },
    {
      "id": "voyage-api",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -600,
      "y": 20,
      "width": 220,
      "height": 80,
      "color": "5",
      "text": "## Voyage AI\nvoyage-3.5-lite\nFree tier (200M tok/mo)"
    },
    {
      "id": "scanner",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -200,
      "y": -400,
      "width": 260,
      "height": 120,
      "color": "1",
      "text": "## Scanner Workers\n`max(1, cores // 3)`\n\n- Pull 500 markets\n- Score: gap, depth, hours\n- Kill 93% -> queue survivors"
    },
    {
      "id": "scan-queue",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 120,
      "y": -380,
      "width": 160,
      "height": 60,
      "color": "6",
      "text": "### scan_queue\n`queue.Queue`"
    },
    {
      "id": "brain",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 340,
      "y": -400,
      "width": 260,
      "height": 140,
      "color": "1",
      "text": "## Brain Workers\n`max(1, cores // 6)`\n\n4 checks via Claude:\n1. Base rate (RAG)\n2. News (6h)\n3. Whale check\n4. Disposition bias\n\n3/4 agree + >75% conf"
    },
    {
      "id": "thesis-queue",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 660,
      "y": -380,
      "width": 160,
      "height": 60,
      "color": "6",
      "text": "### thesis_queue\n`queue.Queue`"
    },
    {
      "id": "executor",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 880,
      "y": -400,
      "width": 260,
      "height": 140,
      "color": "1",
      "text": "## Executor Workers\n`max(1, cores // 24)`\n\nConsensus voting:\n- 2/3 agents = full Kelly\n- 1/3 = half Kelly\n- 0/3 = skip\n\nPaper or live execution"
    },
    {
      "id": "exit-monitor",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 880,
      "y": -180,
      "width": 260,
      "height": 120,
      "color": "1",
      "text": "## Exit Monitor Workers\n`max(1, cores // 6)`\n\n3 triggers:\n1. Target hit (85%)\n2. Volume spike (3x)\n3. Time decay (24h)"
    },
    {
      "id": "strategies",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 880,
      "y": 0,
      "width": 260,
      "height": 100,
      "color": "4",
      "text": "## Strategy Agents\n- **Arbitrage**: price gaps\n- **Convergence**: price -> estimate\n- **Whale Copy**: mirror targets"
    },
    {
      "id": "postgres",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 200,
      "y": -100,
      "width": 300,
      "height": 180,
      "color": "2",
      "text": "## PostgreSQL 17 + pgvector\n\n**Tables:**\n- markets (+ embedding)\n- target_wallets (+ embedding)\n- thesis (+ embedding)\n- positions\n- trade_log\n- historical_outcomes (+ embedding)\n\n**HNSW indexes** on all embeddings"
    },
    {
      "id": "worker-pool",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -200,
      "y": -180,
      "width": 260,
      "height": 80,
      "color": "6",
      "text": "## WorkerPool\nAuto-scales to `os.cpu_count()`\nEnv var overrides\nTarget: 96-thread AMD"
    },
    {
      "id": "cli",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 200,
      "y": 140,
      "width": 300,
      "height": 140,
      "color": "4",
      "text": "## CLI (Click)\n```\npolyagent status [--watch]\npolyagent perf [--daily|--by-strategy]\npolyagent positions [--closed|--worst]\npolyagent markets [--rejected]\npolyagent thesis <MARKET_ID>\n```"
    },
    {
      "id": "container-app",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -200,
      "y": 140,
      "width": 220,
      "height": 80,
      "color": "0",
      "text": "### polyagent-app\nPython 3.14t + Rust CLI\nContainerfile + compose.yaml"
    },
    {
      "id": "container-db",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -200,
      "y": 260,
      "width": 220,
      "height": 60,
      "color": "0",
      "text": "### polyagent-db\nPostgreSQL 17 + pgvector"
    },
    {
      "id": "kelly",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 660,
      "y": -260,
      "width": 160,
      "height": 80,
      "color": "4",
      "text": "### Kelly Criterion\nf* = (p*b - q) / b\nCapped at 0.25\nSweet spot: 0.05-0.15"
    }
  ],
